---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/layout/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Stockade"
  description="Learn how Stockade handles your data. We collect no personal information — all simulation state is stored locally in your browser."
>
  <Navbar />

  <main class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 py-16">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <div class="text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[#f59e0b] mb-3">Legal</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--c-text)] mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[13px] font-mono text-[var(--c-text-subtle)]">Last updated: June 22, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-legal">

      <section>
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          Stockade ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website stockademarketsim.com (the "Service"). This page
          informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when
          you use our Service. We are committed to protecting your privacy. In short: <strong>we collect
          no personally identifiable information</strong> and have no user accounts.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Data We Collect</h2>

        <h3>No Account Required</h3>
        <p>
          Stockade requires no registration, login, or email address. You can use every feature of the
          platform without providing any personal information to us.
        </p>

        <h3>Local Storage (Client-Side Only)</h3>
        <p>
          Your trading simulation state — including your virtual portfolio balance, trade history,
          preferences such as dark/light mode, and other settings — is stored exclusively in your
          browser's <code>localStorage</code>. This data never leaves your device and is never
          transmitted to our servers. You can clear it at any time by clearing your browser's site data.
        </p>

        <h3>Usage Data</h3>
        <p>
          We may collect anonymised, aggregated usage data (such as page views and session counts)
          through standard web analytics tools. This data cannot be used to identify you and is used
          solely to understand how the Service is used and to improve it.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

        <h3>Google Fonts</h3>
        <p>
          Stockade uses fonts (Inter and JetBrains Mono) served by Google Fonts. When your browser
          requests these fonts, your IP address is sent to Google's servers. Please refer to
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Google's Privacy Policy
          </a> for details on how they handle that data.
        </p>

        <h3>Hosting</h3>
        <p>
          The site is hosted on a third-party web hosting provider. Standard web server logs (IP
          address, browser type, referring URL, timestamp) may be retained by the hosting provider in
          accordance with their own privacy policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Stockade does not use tracking cookies or advertising cookies. Your theme preference is stored
          in <code>localStorage</code>, not in a cookie. If future features require session cookies, this
          policy will be updated accordingly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally
          identifiable information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe
          your child has provided us with personal data, please contact us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Links to Other Sites</h2>
        <p>
          Our Service may contain links to third-party websites. We have no control over and assume no
          responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or
          services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by
          updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. You are advised to review this page
          periodically.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@stockademarketsim.com">hello@stockademarketsim.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .prose-legal section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--c-border);
  }
  .prose-legal section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--c-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .prose-legal h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--c-text);
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #f59e0b;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .prose-legal a:hover {
    color: #fbbf24;
  }
  .prose-legal code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85em;
    background: var(--c-bg-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    color: var(--c-text);
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    color: var(--c-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
